{"word":"G280 - ἄμετρος - ámetros - am'-et-ros - Without measure","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄμετρος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ámetros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">am'-et-ros</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without measure</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அளவுக்குமிஞ்சிய, அளவைக்கடந்த - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without measure, immense"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G3358 - μέτρον - métron - met'-ron/3358\">G3358</a>; <i>immoderate:</i> - (thing) without measure.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G280/280\">G280</a>, <a href=\"#/G3354/3354\">G3354</a>, <a href=\"#/G3357/3357\">G3357</a>, <a href=\"#/G3358/3358\">G3358</a>"}]}